msgid "In the Site Editor, open Styles to change colours and typefaces. Nothing you do there can break the theme — experiment freely."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin.php
msgid "This theme is already fast by design: zero front-end JavaScript, self-hosted fonts that don't phone home, and tuning against the Core Web Vitals search engines actually measure."
msgstr ""

#: inc/admin.php
msgid "Accessibility is built in — real focus outlines, a keyboard skip link, sensible heading order, and motion that respects a reduce-motion setting. Keep your own copy and images to that bar and the whole site stays welcoming."
msgstr ""

